<div class=3D"section1 summary" id=3D"S_GUID-8A9B089E-DD4C-4D3A-836F-CFD133=
81B5CC" purpose=3D"summary"><h2>Summary</h2><p id=3D"GUID-8A9B089E-DD4C-4D3=
A-836F-CFD13381B5CC" conrefsub=3D"GUID-E42A26DB-DC07-403E-86CE-84F0E2D4535F=
/GUID-57758E77-6B4A-45D5-903D-AEEBA1F514A4">Identifies the slope (gradient =
or steepness) from each cell of a raster.</p><p id=3D"GUID-188E9A48-8E96-49=
55-8F1C-83D6FDF57622" ishcondition=3D"product_filter=3Dpro"><span class=3D"=
ph">The <span purpose=3D"gptoolref"><a class=3D"xref xref" href=3D"https://=
pro.arcgis.com/en/pro-app/3.4/tool-reference/spatial-analyst/surface-parame=
ters.htm">Surface Parameters</a></span> tool provides a newer implementatio=
n and enhanced functionality.</span></p><p id=3D"GUID-2CBF231A-2723-47A8-B3=
52-68991C8C5279" ishcondition=3D"product_filter=3Dpro"><span class=3D"ph"><=
a class=3D"xref xref" href=3D"https://pro.arcgis.com/en/pro-app/3.4/tool-re=
ference/spatial-analyst/how-slope-works.htm">Learn more about how Slope wor=
ks</a></span></p>


</div>
